---
// HeroCopy: portada arcade con jerarquia de poster.
---

<div class="hero-copy">
  <h1 class="title">
    <span class="title-main" data-moment="title-main">Polla</span>
    <span class="title-accent" data-moment="title-accent">Mundialera</span>
  </h1>

  <p class="subtitle" data-animate="fade-up" style="--i:5">
    <span class="dash" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span>SECPLAN 2026</span>
    <span class="dash" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  </p>

  <p class="description" data-animate="fade-up" style="--i:6">
    El juego interno que une a nuestro equipo. Pronostica, suma puntos y disfruta la ruta hacia la gloria.
  </p>
</div>

<style>
  .hero-copy {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: clamp(0.35rem, 0.9vw, 0.68rem);
    margin-top: clamp(-0.7rem, -0.75vw, -0.35rem);
  }

  .hero-copy::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: -6%;
    top: 2%;
    width: 64%;
    height: 76%;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 28% 42%, var(--pm-cyan-glow), transparent 62%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 64% 70%, var(--pm-gold-glow), transparent 60%);
    filter: blur(34px);
    opacity: 0.85;
    z-index: -1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    .hero-copy::before {
      animation: glowPulse 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
  }

  .title {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--pm-blue-950, #071735);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 9.6vw, 8.8rem);
    font-weight: 950;
    line-height: 0.82;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .title-main {
    color: var(--pm-blue-950, #071735);
    transform: skewX(-5deg);
    transform-origin: left center;
  }

  .title-accent {
    width: fit-content;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, #0863f7 0%, #15a8ff 48%, #005bff 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
    text-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(0, 91, 255, 0.16);
    transform: skewX(-5deg);
    transform-origin: left center;
  }

  .subtitle {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.7rem;
    margin: 0.1rem 0 0;
    color: var(--pm-purple-600);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.6rem);
    font-weight: 950;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .dash {
    display: inline-block;
    width: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.8rem);
    height: 2px;
    background: currentColor;
  }

  .description {
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--pm-blue-900);
    font-size: clamp(0.96rem, 1.25vw, 1.18rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.34;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .title {
      font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 16vw, 5.6rem);
    }

    .subtitle {
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    }

    .description {
      max-width: 34rem;
    }
  }
</style>
